<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Straßburg</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass er nur das Gerücht von der Ankunft König Sigismunds von Ungarn im Reich gehört hat.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_283" id="141r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_283_r2l11">
<add>Den <expan>furſ<ex>ichtigen</ex></expan> <expan>Erſ<ex>amen</ex></expan> <expan>vn<ex>d</ex></expan> <expan>vveẏſe<ex>n</ex></expan> ~ <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> Meiſter</add></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_283_r2l12">
<add>vnd den <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> des <expan>R<ex>ats</ex></expan> der Stat cʒu</add> <expan>Straſſb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> / <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etc </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_283_r2l13"><expan>Lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnde / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> gnedıgen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_283_r2l14">des künigs <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> vngern etc 
<del rend="strikethrough">vvie </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_283_line_1576570168824_1042">daʒ </ab></add> ew vaſt vil geſagt werd / vvie er </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_283_r2l15">von <expan>vng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> her aws <expan>gecʒoge<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> ſe </del> vnd in vnſer Stat kumen ſeÿ / . <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_283_r2l16">auf 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> wege </del> / den wege / Laſſen wir ewr erſame vveiſheit wiſſen / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_283_r2l18">daʒ man beÿ vns lantmanſweiſe auch vil davon ſagt / 
<add><ab facs="#facs_283_r2l17">daʒ er kumen ſülle </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> vnd etlıche <expan>ſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_283_r2l19">
<del rend="strikethrough">er kum / vns etlıche er kum nicht </del> /. vnd wir <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> darnach gevorſchet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_283_r2l20">mit <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>botcheft<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd ſüſt / vnd kunden biſher noch keın eıgenſchaft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_283_r2l21">ervaren / ob er ſich von <expan>vng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> her auf cʒe cʒıehen <expan>erhab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_283_r2l22"> <expan>vnt<ex>er</ex></expan> wegen ſeÿ / 
<del rend="strikethrough">oder nicht </del> / . vnd heten wir ıht eigenſchaft davon </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_283_r2l23">geweſt / Das <expan>het<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> fürſıchtıkeit cʒemal <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> <expan>verſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_283_r2l24">vvan wo etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_283" id="141r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><add>Den <expan>furs<ex>ichtigen</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>ers<ex>amen</ex></expan>
<expan>un<ex>d</ex></expan>
<expan>weyse<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
                            meister</add>
<add>und den <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> des
                                <expan>r<ex>ats</ex></expan> der stat czu</add>
<expan>Strassb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnde, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> gnedigen
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, des künigs <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        Ungern, etc., <add>daz</add> ew vast vil gesagt werd, wie er von
                                <expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> heraws
                            <expan>geczoge<ex>n</ex></expan> und in unser stat kumen sey
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> auf den wege, lassen wir ewr ersame weisheit
                        wissen, daz man bey uns lantmansweise auch vil davon sagt, <add>daz er kumen
                            sülle</add>, und wir <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> darnach gevorschet
                        mit <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>botcheft<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und süst und kunden bisher noch kein
                        eigenschaft ervaren, ob er sich von <expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> herauf
                        cze cziehen <expan>erhab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab und
                            <expan>unt<ex>er</ex></expan> wegen sey. Und heten wir iht eigenschaft
                        davon gewest, das <expan>het<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> fürsichtikeit czemal
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>verschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Wan wo etc.</ab>
</div>
